Replace legacy session-based auth with OAuth 2.0 + PKCE.                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                
## Goals                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                
вЂў Eliminate session token storage issues                                                                                                                        
вЂў Support SSO via SAML/OIDC                                                                                                                                     
