Alex Rivera  вЂў 10 Jan 2025, 09:15                                                                                                                               
Started on the PKCE flow. A few notes from my initial investigation:                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                
1. The existing AuthService interface is too tightly coupled to session tokens вЂ” I'll need                                                                      
to introduce an OAuthProvider abstraction                                                                                                                       
2. Refresh token rotation needs careful thought around race conditions with concurrent                                                                          
requests                                                                                                                                                        
3. The IdP metadata endpoint returns XML which we'll need to parse for SAML support later                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                
I've spiked a branch (feat/oauth-pkce-spike) with the basic authorization URL generation                                                                        
working. Will open a draft PR tomorrow for early feedback.                                                                                                      
